---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import AdminLayout from '../components/layout/AdminLayout';
---

<BaseLayout title="Dokumentasi API">
  <AdminLayout client:load activePage="api_docs" title="Dokumentasi API">
    <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-8">
      
      {/* Left Column: API Documentation */}
      <div class="flex-1 space-y-8 max-w-3xl">
        <div>
          <h1 class="text-xl font-extrabold text-zinc-900 dark:text-white tracking-tight">
            Dokumentasi Developer API
          </h1>
          <p class="text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400 mt-1">
            Gunakan REST API AUTOIN untuk mengirim pesan secara otomatis langsung dari program atau website backend Anda.
          </p>
        </div>

        {/* Section 1: Authentication */}
        <div class="space-y-3">
          <h2 class="text-sm font-bold text-zinc-800 dark:text-zinc-200 flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="w-5 h-5 rounded-lg bg-blue-500/10 text-blue-500 flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] font-bold">1</span>
            Autentikasi Token
          </h2>
          <p class="text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed">
            Seluruh request API wajib menyertakan HTTP header <code class="px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded bg-zinc-100 dark:bg-zinc-800/80 font-mono text-[10px] text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400">Authorization: Bearer &lt;YOUR_API_KEY&gt;</code>. 
            Anda dapat memperoleh API Key melalui halaman pengaturan Kredensial API Key di dashboard ini. Key yang dihasilkan akan diawali dengan prefix <code class="px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded bg-zinc-100 dark:bg-zinc-800/80 font-mono text-[10px]">autoin_</code>.
          </p>
        </div>

        {/* Section 2: Get Channels */}
        <div class="space-y-3">
          <h2 class="text-sm font-bold text-zinc-800 dark:text-zinc-200 flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="w-5 h-5 rounded-lg bg-blue-500/10 text-blue-500 flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] font-bold">2</span>
            Mendapatkan ID Channel
          </h2>
          <p class="text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed">
            Sebelum mengirimkan pesan, Anda perlu mengetahui list device atau channel sosial media yang aktif di akun Anda. Gunakan endpoint ini untuk melihat list channel beserta parameter ID-nya.
          </p>

          <div class="bg-zinc-50 dark:bg-[#0e0e11] p-4 rounded-xl border border-zinc-200 dark:border-zinc-800/80 space-y-2">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded bg-emerald-500/10 text-emerald-500 text-[9px] font-extrabold uppercase">GET</span>
              <span class="font-mono text-xs text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-300">/api/channels</span>
            </div>
            <div class="text-[10px] text-zinc-400 dark:text-zinc-500 font-mono">
              Response format: Array of Channel objects.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        {/* Section 3: Send Broadcast */}
        <div class="space-y-3">
          <h2 class="text-sm font-bold text-zinc-800 dark:text-zinc-200 flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="w-5 h-5 rounded-lg bg-blue-500/10 text-blue-500 flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] font-bold">3</span>
            Mengirimkan Broadcast Campaign
          </h2>
          <p class="text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed">
            Kirim request POST ke endpoint ini dengan payload JSON untuk membuat draf broadcast. Lanjutkan dengan trigger pengiriman untuk mendistribusikan pesan ke seluruh channel.
          </p>

          <div class="bg-zinc-50 dark:bg-[#0e0e11] p-4 rounded-xl border border-zinc-200 dark:border-zinc-800/80 space-y-3">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded bg-blue-500/10 text-blue-500 text-[9px] font-extrabold uppercase">POST</span>
              <span class="font-mono text-xs text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-300">/api/broadcasts</span>
            </div>
            
            <div class="border-t border-zinc-200/40 dark:border-zinc-800/40 pt-3 space-y-1.5">
              <span class="block text-[10px] font-bold text-zinc-450 dark:text-zinc-500 uppercase tracking-widest">Parameter Body (JSON)</span>
              <table class="w-full text-left text-xs border-collapse">
                <thead>
                  <tr class="text-[10px] text-zinc-400 dark:text-zinc-500 uppercase tracking-wider border-b border-zinc-200/40 dark:border-zinc-800/40">
                    <th class="pb-1.5 font-bold">Field</th>
                    <th class="pb-1.5 font-bold">Tipe</th>
                    <th class="pb-1.5 font-bold">Deskripsi</th>
                  </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody class="divide-y divide-zinc-200/20 dark:divide-zinc-800/20 text-[11px] text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-455 font-sans">
                  <tr>
                    <td class="py-2 font-mono text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-300 font-bold">content</td>
                    <td class="py-2 text-blue-500 font-mono">string</td>
                    <td class="py-2">Pesan teks utama (Mendukung HTML tags). *Wajib</td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td class="py-2 font-mono text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-300 font-bold">channel_ids</td>
                    <td class="py-2 text-blue-500 font-mono">array</td>
                    <td class="py-2">List ID target channel dari endpoint GET /api/channels. *Wajib</td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td class="py-2 font-mono text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-300">title</td>
                    <td class="py-2 text-blue-500 font-mono">string</td>
                    <td class="py-2">Judul kampanye broadcast (Opsional).</td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td class="py-2 font-mono text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-300">media_url</td>
                    <td class="py-2 text-blue-500 font-mono">string</td>
                    <td class="py-2">URL lampiran file/gambar (Opsional).</td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td class="py-2 font-mono text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-300">media_type</td>
                    <td class="py-2 text-blue-500 font-mono">string</td>
                    <td class="py-2">Tipe lampiran: <code class="px-1 py-0.2 rounded bg-zinc-100 dark:bg-zinc-800 text-[10px]">image, video, pdf, document</code>.</td>
                  </tr>
                </tbody>
              </table>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        {/* Section 4: Send Single Message */}
        <div class="space-y-3">
          <h2 class="text-sm font-bold text-zinc-800 dark:text-zinc-200 flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="w-5 h-5 rounded-lg bg-blue-500/10 text-blue-500 flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] font-bold">4</span>
            Mengirimkan Pesan Tunggal (Single Send)
          </h2>
          <p class="text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed">
            Gunakan endpoint ini untuk mengirim pesan langsung (teks & media) ke nomor tujuan tunggal secara instan. Sangat ideal untuk kebutuhan notifikasi transaksional, OTP, invoice, atau chatbot.
          </p>

          <div class="bg-zinc-50 dark:bg-[#0e0e11] p-4 rounded-xl border border-zinc-200 dark:border-zinc-800/80 space-y-3">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded bg-blue-500/10 text-blue-500 text-[9px] font-extrabold uppercase">POST</span>
              <span class="font-mono text-xs text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-300">/api/whatsapp/&#123;channel_id&#125;/send</span>
            </div>
            
            <div class="border-t border-zinc-200/40 dark:border-zinc-800/40 pt-3 space-y-1.5">
              <span class="block text-[10px] font-bold text-zinc-450 dark:text-zinc-500 uppercase tracking-widest">Parameter Body (JSON)</span>
              <table class="w-full text-left text-xs border-collapse">
                <thead>
                  <tr class="text-[10px] text-zinc-400 dark:text-zinc-500 uppercase tracking-wider border-b border-zinc-200/40 dark:border-zinc-800/40">
                    <th class="pb-1.5 font-bold">Field</th>
                    <th class="pb-1.5 font-bold">Tipe</th>
                    <th class="pb-1.5 font-bold">Deskripsi</th>
                  </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody class="divide-y divide-zinc-200/20 dark:divide-zinc-800/20 text-[11px] text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-455 font-sans">
                  <tr>
                    <td class="py-2 font-mono text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-300 font-bold">to</td>
                    <td class="py-2 text-blue-500 font-mono">string</td>
                    <td class="py-2">Nomor WhatsApp tujuan (format: <code class="px-1.5 py-0.2 rounded bg-zinc-100 dark:bg-zinc-800 font-mono text-[10px]">628xxxxxx</code>). *Wajib</td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td class="py-2 font-mono text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-300">message</td>
                    <td class="py-2 text-blue-500 font-mono">string</td>
                    <td class="py-2">Pesan teks utama (dapat dikosongkan jika melampirkan media).</td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td class="py-2 font-mono text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-300">mediaUrl</td>
                    <td class="py-2 text-blue-500 font-mono">string</td>
                    <td class="py-2">URL lampiran file/gambar (Opsional).</td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td class="py-2 font-mono text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-300">mediaType</td>
                    <td class="py-2 text-blue-500 font-mono">string</td>
                    <td class="py-2">Tipe lampiran: <code class="px-1 py-0.2 rounded bg-zinc-100 dark:bg-zinc-800 text-[10px]">image, video, pdf, document</code>.</td>
                  </tr>
                </tbody>
              </table>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      {/* Right Column: Code Playgrounds */}
      <div class="w-full lg:w-96 shrink-0 bg-white dark:bg-[#0e0e11] border border-zinc-200 dark:border-zinc-800/80 rounded-2xl p-5 shadow-sm space-y-4 h-fit text-left">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-1.5">
            <span class="text-xs font-bold text-zinc-800 dark:text-zinc-100 uppercase tracking-wider">Playground Contoh</span>
          </div>
          
          {/* Tab Button Selector */}
          <div class="flex gap-1 bg-zinc-100 dark:bg-zinc-900 p-0.5 rounded-lg text-[9px] font-bold">
            <button data-lang-tab="curl" class="px-1.5 py-1 rounded transition-all capitalize cursor-pointer bg-white dark:bg-zinc-800 text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 shadow-sm">
              cURL
            </button>
            <button data-lang-tab="javascript" class="px-1.5 py-1 rounded transition-all capitalize cursor-pointer text-zinc-400">
              JS
            </button>
            <button data-lang-tab="php" class="px-1.5 py-1 rounded transition-all capitalize cursor-pointer text-zinc-400">
              PHP
            </button>
            <button data-lang-tab="python" class="px-1.5 py-1 rounded transition-all capitalize cursor-pointer text-zinc-400">
              Python
            </button>
          </div>
        </div>

        {/* Snippets Area */}
        <div class="space-y-4">
          
          {/* 1. Auth Headers */}
          <div class="space-y-1.5">
            <span class="block text-[9px] font-bold text-zinc-400 dark:text-zinc-500 uppercase tracking-widest">1. Tes Autentikasi</span>
            
            <pre data-lang-code="curl" class="bg-blue-50/50 dark:bg-zinc-900 p-3 rounded-xl border border-blue-100 dark:border-zinc-850 text-[9px] font-mono text-blue-950 dark:text-zinc-350 overflow-x-auto">curl -X GET https://api.autoin.my.id/api/me \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer autoin_YOUR_API_KEY"</pre>
            
            <pre data-lang-code="javascript" class="hidden bg-blue-50/50 dark:bg-zinc-900 p-3 rounded-xl border border-blue-100 dark:border-zinc-850 text-[9px] font-mono text-blue-950 dark:text-zinc-350 overflow-x-auto">fetch('https://api.autoin.my.id/api/me', &#123;
  headers: &#123;
    'Authorization': 'Bearer autoin_YOUR_API_KEY',
    'Content-Type': 'application/json'
  &#125;
&#125;)
.then(res => res.json())
.then(data => console.log(data));</pre>

            <pre data-lang-code="php" class="hidden bg-blue-50/50 dark:bg-zinc-900 p-3 rounded-xl border border-blue-100 dark:border-zinc-850 text-[9px] font-mono text-blue-950 dark:text-zinc-350 overflow-x-auto">&lt;?php
$ch = curl_init('https://api.autoin.my.id/api/me');
curl_setopt($ch, CURLOPT_RETURNTRANSFER, true);
curl_setopt($ch, CURLOPT_HTTPHEADER, [
    'Authorization: Bearer autoin_YOUR_API_KEY',
    'Content-Type: application/json'
]);
$response = curl_exec($ch);
$data = json_decode($response, true);</pre>

            <pre data-lang-code="python" class="hidden bg-blue-50/50 dark:bg-zinc-900 p-3 rounded-xl border border-blue-100 dark:border-zinc-850 text-[9px] font-mono text-blue-950 dark:text-zinc-350 overflow-x-auto">import requests

headers = &#123;
    'Authorization': 'Bearer autoin_YOUR_API_KEY',
    'Content-Type': 'application/json'
&#125;
response = requests.get('https://api.autoin.my.id/api/me', headers=headers)
print(response.json())</pre>
          </div>

          {/* 2. List Channels */}
          <div class="space-y-1.5">
            <span class="block text-[9px] font-bold text-zinc-400 dark:text-zinc-500 uppercase tracking-widest">2. List Channels</span>
            
            <pre data-lang-code="curl" class="bg-blue-50/50 dark:bg-zinc-900 p-3 rounded-xl border border-blue-100 dark:border-zinc-850 text-[9px] font-mono text-blue-950 dark:text-zinc-350 overflow-x-auto">curl -X GET https://api.autoin.my.id/api/channels \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer autoin_YOUR_API_KEY"</pre>
            
            <pre data-lang-code="javascript" class="hidden bg-blue-50/50 dark:bg-zinc-900 p-3 rounded-xl border border-blue-100 dark:border-zinc-850 text-[9px] font-mono text-blue-950 dark:text-zinc-350 overflow-x-auto">fetch('https://api.autoin.my.id/api/channels', &#123;
  headers: &#123; 'Authorization': 'Bearer autoin_YOUR_API_KEY' &#125;
&#125;)
.then(res => res.json())
.then(channels => console.log(channels));</pre>

            <pre data-lang-code="php" class="hidden bg-blue-50/50 dark:bg-zinc-900 p-3 rounded-xl border border-blue-100 dark:border-zinc-850 text-[9px] font-mono text-blue-950 dark:text-zinc-350 overflow-x-auto">&lt;?php
$ch = curl_init('https://api.autoin.my.id/api/channels');
curl_setopt($ch, CURLOPT_RETURNTRANSFER, true);
curl_setopt($ch, CURLOPT_HTTPHEADER, [
    'Authorization: Bearer autoin_YOUR_API_KEY'
]);
$response = curl_exec($ch);
$channels = json_decode($response, true);</pre>

            <pre data-lang-code="python" class="hidden bg-blue-50/50 dark:bg-zinc-900 p-3 rounded-xl border border-blue-100 dark:border-zinc-850 text-[9px] font-mono text-blue-950 dark:text-zinc-350 overflow-x-auto">import requests

headers = &#123;'Authorization': 'Bearer autoin_YOUR_API_KEY'&#125;
response = requests.get('https://api.autoin.my.id/api/channels', headers=headers)
print(response.json())</pre>
          </div>

          {/* 3. Send Broadcast */}
          <div class="space-y-1.5">
            <span class="block text-[9px] font-bold text-zinc-400 dark:text-zinc-500 uppercase tracking-widest">3. Kirim Broadcast</span>
            
            <pre data-lang-code="curl" class="bg-blue-50/50 dark:bg-zinc-900 p-3 rounded-xl border border-blue-100 dark:border-zinc-850 text-[9px] font-mono text-blue-950 dark:text-zinc-350 overflow-x-auto">curl -X POST https://api.autoin.my.id/api/broadcasts \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer autoin_YOUR_API_KEY" \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '&#123;
    "title": "Promo Weekend",
    "content": "Diskon 50% khusus hari ini!",
    "channel_ids": [1, 2],
    "media_url": "https://example.com/image.jpg",
    "media_type": "image"
  &#125;'</pre>
            
            <pre data-lang-code="javascript" class="hidden bg-blue-50/50 dark:bg-zinc-900 p-3 rounded-xl border border-blue-100 dark:border-zinc-850 text-[9px] font-mono text-blue-950 dark:text-zinc-350 overflow-x-auto">fetch('https://api.autoin.my.id/api/broadcasts', &#123;
  method: 'POST',
  headers: &#123;
    'Authorization': 'Bearer autoin_YOUR_API_KEY',
    'Content-Type': 'application/json'
  &#125;,
  body: JSON.stringify(&#123;
    title: 'Promo Weekend',
    content: 'Diskon 50% khusus hari ini!',
    channel_ids: [1, 2],
    media_url: 'https://example.com/image.jpg',
    media_type: 'image'
  &#125;)
&#125;)</pre>

            <pre data-lang-code="php" class="hidden bg-blue-50/50 dark:bg-zinc-900 p-3 rounded-xl border border-blue-100 dark:border-zinc-850 text-[9px] font-mono text-blue-950 dark:text-zinc-350 overflow-x-auto">&lt;?php
$payload = [
    'title' => 'Promo Weekend',
    'content' => 'Diskon 50% khusus hari ini!',
    'channel_ids' => [1, 2],
    'media_url' => 'https://example.com/image.jpg',
    'media_type' => 'image'
];

$ch = curl_init('https://api.autoin.my.id/api/broadcasts');
curl_setopt($ch, CURLOPT_RETURNTRANSFER, true);
curl_setopt($ch, CURLOPT_POST, true);
curl_setopt($ch, CURLOPT_POSTFIELDS, json_encode($payload));
curl_setopt($ch, CURLOPT_HTTPHEADER, [
    'Authorization: Bearer autoin_YOUR_API_KEY',
    'Content-Type: application/json'
]);
$response = curl_exec($ch);
$result = json_decode($response, true);</pre>

            <pre data-lang-code="python" class="hidden bg-blue-50/50 dark:bg-zinc-900 p-3 rounded-xl border border-blue-100 dark:border-zinc-850 text-[9px] font-mono text-blue-950 dark:text-zinc-350 overflow-x-auto">import requests

payload = &#123;
    'title': 'Promo Weekend',
    'content': 'Diskon 50% khusus hari ini!',
    'channel_ids': [1, 2],
    'media_url': 'https://example.com/image.jpg',
    'media_type': 'image'
&#125;
headers = &#123;
    'Authorization': 'Bearer autoin_YOUR_API_KEY',
    'Content-Type': 'application/json'
&#125;
response = requests.post('https://api.autoin.my.id/api/broadcasts', json=payload, headers=headers)
print(response.json())</pre>
          </div>

          {/* 4. Send Single Message */}
          <div class="space-y-1.5">
            <span class="block text-[9px] font-bold text-zinc-400 dark:text-zinc-500 uppercase tracking-widest">4. Kirim Pesan Tunggal</span>
            
            <pre data-lang-code="curl" class="bg-blue-50/50 dark:bg-zinc-900 p-3 rounded-xl border border-blue-100 dark:border-zinc-850 text-[9px] font-mono text-blue-950 dark:text-zinc-350 overflow-x-auto">curl -X POST https://api.autoin.my.id/api/whatsapp/YOUR_CHANNEL_ID/send \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer autoin_YOUR_API_KEY" \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '&#123;
    "to": "628123456789",
    "message": "Halo! Ini adalah notifikasi otomatis.",
    "mediaUrl": "https://example.com/invoice.pdf",
    "mediaType": "pdf"
  &#125;'</pre>
            
            <pre data-lang-code="javascript" class="hidden bg-blue-50/50 dark:bg-zinc-900 p-3 rounded-xl border border-blue-100 dark:border-zinc-850 text-[9px] font-mono text-blue-950 dark:text-zinc-350 overflow-x-auto">fetch('https://api.autoin.my.id/api/whatsapp/YOUR_CHANNEL_ID/send', &#123;
  method: 'POST',
  headers: &#123;
    'Authorization': 'Bearer autoin_YOUR_API_KEY',
    'Content-Type': 'application/json'
  &#125;,
  body: JSON.stringify(&#123;
    to: '628123456789',
    message: 'Halo! Ini adalah notifikasi otomatis.',
    mediaUrl: 'https://example.com/invoice.pdf',
    mediaType: 'pdf'
  &#125;)
&#125;)</pre>

            <pre data-lang-code="php" class="hidden bg-blue-50/50 dark:bg-zinc-900 p-3 rounded-xl border border-blue-100 dark:border-zinc-850 text-[9px] font-mono text-blue-950 dark:text-zinc-350 overflow-x-auto">&lt;?php
$payload = [
    'to' => '628123456789',
    'message' => 'Halo! Ini adalah notifikasi otomatis.',
    'mediaUrl' => 'https://example.com/invoice.pdf',
    'mediaType' => 'pdf'
];

$ch = curl_init('https://api.autoin.my.id/api/whatsapp/YOUR_CHANNEL_ID/send');
curl_setopt($ch, CURLOPT_RETURNTRANSFER, true);
curl_setopt($ch, CURLOPT_POST, true);
curl_setopt($ch, CURLOPT_POSTFIELDS, json_encode($payload));
curl_setopt($ch, CURLOPT_HTTPHEADER, [
    'Authorization: Bearer autoin_YOUR_API_KEY',
    'Content-Type: application/json'
]);
$response = curl_exec($ch);
$result = json_decode($response, true);</pre>

            <pre data-lang-code="python" class="hidden bg-blue-50/50 dark:bg-zinc-900 p-3 rounded-xl border border-blue-100 dark:border-zinc-850 text-[9px] font-mono text-blue-950 dark:text-zinc-350 overflow-x-auto">import requests

payload = &#123;
    'to': '628123456789',
    'message': 'Halo! Ini adalah notifikasi otomatis.',
    'mediaUrl': 'https://example.com/invoice.pdf',
    'mediaType': 'pdf'
&#125;
headers = &#123;
    'Authorization': 'Bearer autoin_YOUR_API_KEY',
    'Content-Type': 'application/json'
&#125;
response = requests.post('https://api.autoin.my.id/api/whatsapp/YOUR_CHANNEL_ID/send', json=payload, headers=headers)
print(response.json())</pre>

          {/* Response Explanation */}
          <div class="mt-4 p-4 bg-blue-500/5 dark:bg-blue-500/5 border border-blue-500/10 rounded-xl space-y-2">
            <h4 class="text-xs font-bold text-blue-650 dark:text-blue-400 flex items-center gap-1">
              <span>💡</span> Cara Mengecek Status Pengiriman Sukses
            </h4>
            <p class="text-[11px] text-zinc-550 dark:text-zinc-450 leading-relaxed">
              Jika pesan berhasil dikirimkan ke antrean WhatsApp, API akan mengembalikan status <strong>HTTP 200 OK</strong> dengan response body mengandung <code class="px-1 py-0.5 rounded bg-zinc-100 dark:bg-zinc-850 font-mono text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400">"ok": true</code>.
            </p>
            <p class="text-[11px] text-zinc-550 dark:text-zinc-455 leading-relaxed">
              Status <code class="px-1 py-0.5 rounded bg-zinc-100 dark:bg-zinc-850 font-mono">"status": "PENDING"</code> di dalam objek result menandakan bahwa pesan telah sukses terbuat di socket client (Baileys) dan sedang dikirimkan secara instan ke nomor tujuan. Anda dapat menganggap response ini sebagai <strong>transaksi sukses</strong>.
            </p>
            <pre class="bg-blue-50/50 dark:bg-zinc-950 p-3 rounded-xl border border-blue-100 dark:border-zinc-850 text-[9px] font-mono text-blue-900 dark:text-blue-400/90 overflow-x-auto">&#123;23;
